title: BRIEF-Esprinet unit Nilox signs distribution agreement with Manfrotto
text:
BRIEF-Esprinet unit Nilox signs distribution agreement with Manfrotto Sept 10 
Sept 10 Esprinet SpA : 
* Unit Nilox signs agreement with Manfrotto for distribution in Italy, US, France And United Kingdom of Nilox's technology for sport
